---
title: Roasted Cauliflower Bengal Biryani with Currants & Yoghurt
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the rice itself is cooked with the curry paste? Now that’s magical. Studded
with sweet currants, refreshing herbs and roasted cauliflower, this dish packs flavour in every bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

